        <mxCell id="eamBAlu2UB9TC6nft0BU-178" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Information Screen &lt;/b&gt;- Landing screen of the application&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Contracts Screen - &lt;/b&gt;List view of contracts with filters.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Project Overview Screen - &lt;/b&gt;Read-only List view of contracts with filters, can add a new item.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Review resource Screen - &lt;/b&gt;Detail view of the item. Can delete and edit the existing item (Except on the Review Project Screen)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Resource Screen -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;Each screen directly connected to a SharePoint list can view a list of items from that list. From this screen the user can select a specific item to access the &quot;Review&quot; Screen and add a new item." vertex="1">
